        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            Classic cars evoke a sense of nostalgia, history, and craftsmanship. These machines are not just vehicles; they are works of art that have stood the test of time. From the roaring engines to the gleaming chrome, classic cars symbolize a bygone era of automotive engineering that modern cars often cannot replicate. In this post, we will explore the top 10 classic cars that have captured the hearts of car enthusiasts worldwide. These cars are celebrated for their beauty, performance, and the stories they tell.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Ferrari 250 GTO</h2>
        <p>
